snippet.title: Trauma Talk
snippet.description:
You're not weird, and you're not alone. Trauma Talk is a channel for exploring and discussing life in the aftermath of trauma, be it sexual assault, domestic violence, emotional/mental/spiritual abuse, natural disasters, combat, or any other type of trauma. You are welcome here - and you're never alone. I am not a therapist, but I am simply speaking from my own experiences as someone who has lived through these things myself.

You are incredible - for being here to read this, for staying alive, and for looking for light.

My P.O. Box:
Jo Beckwith 
3578 Hartsel Drive #615
Colorado Springs, CO 80920
